Leadership Focus Group in EB CFpst INVITATION Chairperson Tom Wilbeck Invitees Deirdre McCaffrey Peter F Keavey Jennifer Shipos Michelle Bruce John Swinney Stuart Donaldson Teresa Callahan Lori Pinder Tai Nguyen Karen Snow Bryce Baxter Ross Mesquita Jodi Coulter Corry Bentley Jim Meyn Regan Smith Kenneth M Harmon John D Powell Date Time AM AM Central Standard Time Room EB CECT Description Leadership Focus Group in EB C Detailed Description When Thursday May AM AM GMT Central Time US Canada Where EB C Hello managers and supervisors Because of your excellent managerial skills youve been selected by your HR community to share your insight in a focus group discussion on Thursday May th from til in EB C We have a customized Managers level leadership class coming in June and your input on Thursday will help shape this offering to provide the most benefit to its attendees The focus group will be facilitated by Enrons partner in this leadership venture PDI Personnel Decisions International Your input is greatly appreciated and needed Please reply to this invitation and let me know if you will attend Should you have any questions or concerns please contact Tom Wilbeck with the EWS training group Thank you for your support in this venture

MA bluffers in EB CHR Bluffers guide is back again The HR Bluffers Guide to the Business is a great opportunity for HR professionals to learn about our business and HR operations without getting bogged down in the details These classes are a quick and dirty way of getting enough information about certain topics to make a real difference real fast On Tuesday March th at Michelle Cash will present on the topic of Mergers and Acquisitions This class promises to offer valuable information that could help today The class is free and guess whatWell provide lunch too You have no reason to miss this great learning opportunity Please RSVP ASAPOK

Netowrking communityThis is a great easy to use site Even if youre a member of another networking community its always a good idea to sign up for more Good Luck Tom Wilbeck Organizational Development and Learning Original Message From Prihoda Melissa Sent Monday December AM To Wilbeck Tom Subject FW Networking Community Hey guys here is a networking community a group of us put together Feel free to share it The doc attached is how you register for the distribution list Melissa XENEs Networking community of current or former employees who are looking for employment or have information regarding employment opportunities Please share the following information in your first message to the community name personal email address home phone numberoptional
